{"tid":1240432,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"大家唔好鬆懈同跌入同暖層","createTime":"2019-06-18T10:39:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T10:55:12.000Z","uid":10206,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"298da306cc535df9b5ceae4f0040b729a564c1a4","tid":1240432,"uid":10206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T10:39:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jYcO7ui.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjYcO7ui.png&h=1d152377&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AjnSPKR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAjnSPKR.png&h=12d6fd23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n岩岩搭火車隔離廢老仲睇緊支持警犬嘅文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為佢唔係用iPhone 所以我冇得即時airdrop長輩圖比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢兩日見到好多手足開post講咩星期日要有300萬人曬政府馬同埋日日都圍鳩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n冇錯我都好認同<br />\n短期內我地聲勢好大<br />\n而今次學到嘅進步同團結亦令大家好鼓舞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但要記住到目前為止我地係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">乜 都 未 贏 到</span></span><br />\n<br />\n但如果需要更多人，先唔講人數比上次更多<br />\n政府扮讓步嘅情況下要保住200萬人其實都唔係一件容易嘅事<br />\n大家要繼續好似69之前咁保持當時嘅宣傳同動員力唔可以鬆懈<br />\n<br />\n而家條柒婆連200萬人都唔撚驚<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">一鬆懈就會我地只會變成一個200萬人嘅同暖層</span><br />\n<br />\n大家一齊努力星期五見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db0ed694368711689b6164c895c7dc50f1f25325","tid":1240432,"uid":10206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T10:42:03.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"d75995e34079867d5c635d88dafc7e15c1e1b4f1","tid":1240432,"uid":10206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T10:44:59.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"ffb974a506af567e4f0e425ad6eeb3b35f8e5081","tid":1240432,"uid":10206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T10:49:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"899cc0443d5a098687cfd6aaf6c5f1a29e61bbb9","tid":1240432,"uid":10206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T10:55:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}